name: Pegasus Canyon
description:
Introduction

was not able to finish this canyon after getting cliffed out on the unknown approach. Took photos and wrote up a trip report about our failed exploration on 1-2-16, and stated that we would be back soon to finish it.

UPDATE: This canyon was completed by another party of three a few weeks after our attempt and recorded that the big rappel in it was 320'

Background

Attempted to do this canyon 1-2-16, and posted album , including this canyon. and stated in the report that we would come back to finish it after getting cliffed-out and bailed. Scott Swaney, & Dave Red & Daniel Elson
